data.description:
Discover the perfect blend of comfort and investment potential in this 6-bedroom, 2-bathroom ranch-style home, just minutes from downtown Denver. Featuring two separate units on the main and lower levels, each equipped with updated kitchens, this property offers versatility for both homeowners and potential renters. The main floor boasts a modern open-concept design with three bedrooms, while the lower level mirrors the style and functionality, offering an additional three bedrooms. Each unit enjoys its own private driveway and entrance, ensuring convenience and privacy. The well-maintained exterior and spacious backyard enhance the appeal of this property, making it an ideal residence for a growing family or a lucrative investment opportunity.

With contemporary finishes and dual entrances, this home seamlessly combines style and practicality. Whether you choose to reside in one unit and lease the other or simply enjoy the expansive living space, this ranch-style gem provides a rare opportunity to experience the best of both worlds which is minutes away from downtown Denver. Don't miss out on the chance to call this updated and versatile property your home, offering a perfect balance between modern living and rental potential.
